    <title>Digraphs with at most one trivial critical ideal</title>
    <summary>  Critical ideals generalize the critical group, Smith group and the
characteristic polynomials of the adjacency and Laplacian matrices of a graph.
We give a complete characterization of the digraphs with at most one trivial
critical ideal. Which implies the characterizations of the digraphs whose
critical group has one invariant factor equal to one, and the digraphs whose
Smith group has one invariant factor equal to one.
</summary>
